ury-old-market-biden-is-president-not-bibi/0000018b-2040-d010-a59f-b961f1a00000</guid></item><item><title>在伦敦和纽约：传播以色列信息的创意举措</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/in-london-and-new-york-guerrilla-campaigns-to-spread-israels-message/0000018b-208e-d010-a59f-b9ef1bd30000</link><description>居住在国外的以色列涂鸦艺术家和设计师决定发挥创意，提高人们对被绑架到加沙的以色列人的认识</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:04:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/in-london-and-new-york-guerrilla-campaigns-to-spread-israels-message/0000018b-208e-d010-a59f-b9ef1bd30000</guid></item><item><title>向我的美国朋友解释我为什么留在以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/explaining-to-my-american-friend-why-im-staying-in-israel/0000018b-230e-d680-af9b-23ce83a80000</link><description>“如果不是为了你自己，那就为了你的孩子，走吧，”她告诉我。逻辑尖叫着她是对的，但我们大多数人不适合倾听</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 09:40:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/explaining-to-my-american-friend-why-im-staying-in-israel/0000018b-230e-d680-af9b-23ce83a80000</guid></item><item><title>“没有人梦想我们需要这么大的地方”来辨认以色列遇难者的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/no-one-dreamed-wed-need-such-a-big-place-to-identify-israeli-victims-bodies/0000018b-2089-d53b-af8b-73fd95a80000</link><description>熟悉该中心辨认哈马斯袭击受害者尸体的人士描述，由于尸体众多、涉及机构众多、缺乏明确的管理和专业指导，情况严峻。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 09:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/no-one-dreamed-wed-need-such-a-big-place-to-identify-israeli-victims-bodies/0000018b-2089-d53b-af8b-73fd95a80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在加沙战争中的政治失误是所有错误中最严重的错误</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-netanyahus-political-screw-up-amid-gaza-war-is-the-worst-blunder-of-all/0000018b-208b-d680-af