inet-and-bidens-pledges-strengthen-israels-hand/0000018b-2087-d010-a59f-b9e7ff850000</guid></item><item><title>“我也是作为犹太人来到这里”：布林肯与内塔尼亚胡一起承诺“美国支持以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-gaza-overnight-prioritizing-attacks-on-senior-officials/0000018b-221a-d010-a59f-bb7bf0400000</link><description>周四，以色列与哈马斯的战争进入第六天，死亡人数升至 1,200 多人 ■ 以色列国防军对加沙地带进行连夜空袭，巴勒斯坦人报告数十人死亡 ■ 以色列军队向北部边境派遣部队 ■ 内塔尼亚胡、甘茨组建紧急政府t</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 05:18:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-gaza-overnight-prioritizing-attacks-on-senior-officials/0000018b-221a-d010-a59f-bb7bf0400000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击几天后，特朗普猛烈抨击以色列：“我永远不会忘记比比让我们失望”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/trump-slams-israel-days-after-hamas-attacks-ill-never-forget-bibi-let-us-down/0000018b-21bc-dd34-afdf-f5bf30720000</link><description>特朗普在一次竞选集会上反思以色列在 2020 年 1 月暗杀伊朗革命卫队将军卡西姆·苏莱马尼事件中所扮演的角色时表示，“我想说，这是一件非常可怕的事情”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 03:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/trump-slams-israel-days-after-hamas-attacks-ill-never-forget-bibi-let-us-down/0000018b-21bc-dd34-afdf-f5bf30720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列赫茨尔山军事公墓成为死亡传送带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-mount-herzl-military-cemetery-becomes-a-conveyor-belt-of-death/0000018b-213b-d010-a59f-b97b95ba0000</link><description>葬礼一一举行。志愿者在夜间挖出的数十个新坟墓中传出哀悼声，空气中弥漫着拉比·库克的名言，以及对年轻爱情和足球的回忆。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 00:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-mount-herzl-military-cemetery-becomes-a-conveyor-belt-of-death/0000018b-213b-d010-a59f-b97b95ba0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者不会暂停在西岸的驱逐和剥夺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-pausing-the-expulsion-and-dispossession-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-205f-d680-af9b-22df9b140000</link><description>当以色列和世界关注周六的暴行时，定居者及其支持者正在努力实现他们事实上吞并西岸的梦想</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 00:10:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-pausing-the-expulsion-and-dispossession-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-205f-d680-af9b-22df9b140000</guid></item><item><title>清算必须落在哈马斯身上，而不是所有加沙人身上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-reckoning-must-be-with-hamas-not-with-all-gazans/0000018b-2020-d53b-af8b-737c1b7a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 23:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-reckoning-must-be-with-hamas-not-with-all-gazans/0000018b-2020-d53b-af8b-737c1b7a0000</guid></item><item><title>向内塔尼亚胡先生提出 20 个问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/20-questions-for-mr-netanyahu/0000018b-201d-d010-a59f-b97da86e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 23:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/20-questions-for-mr-netanyahu/0000018b-201d-d010-a59f-b97da86e0000</guid></item><item><title>学生对哈马斯的声援引起了美国校园里年轻犹太人的恐惧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/students-solidarity-with-hamas-raises-fears-among-young-jews-on-campuses-across-the-u-s/0000018b-208c-dd34-afdf-f58f74950000</link><description>巴勒斯坦正义学生组织将哈马斯武装分子周六实施的大规模谋杀描述为“巴勒斯坦抵抗运动的历史性胜利”。纽约大学学生律师协会表示“以色列对这一巨大生命损失负全部责任”</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 22:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/students-solidarity-with-hamas-raises-fears-among-young-jews-on-campuses-across-the-u-s/0000018b-208c-dd34-afdf-f58f74950000</guid></item><item><title>拜登情绪激动地告诉美国犹太领导人：“我拒绝在‘大屠杀以来犹太人最致命的一天’保持沉默”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-emotionally-tells-u-s-jewish-leaders-i-refuse-to-be-silent/0000018b-20a2-d010-a59f-b9e3776d0000</link><description>拜登还强调了美国在袭击事件发生后向以色列提供的军事援助，以及为解救加沙哈马斯扣押的人质所做的努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 22:25:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-emotionally-tells-u-s-jewish-leaders-i-refuse-to-be-silent/0000018b-20a2-d010-a59f-b9e3776d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境的以色列军队观察员：“他们拍摄了我们的相机，我们什么也看不见”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</link><description>在一份录制的证词中，一名士兵讲述了她和她的朋友们如何在外面的恐怖分子试图闯入的情况下躲藏了几个小时。据她说，观察系统遭到枪击并被禁用，以防止它们被发现</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 21:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</guid></item><item><title>“真正的灵魂伴侣”在加沙附近的战场上被哈马斯枪杀——他们的家人忙着寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</link><description>朱迪·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judi Weinstein Haggai) 打电话说，周六早上，她和她的丈夫在基布兹附近遭到枪击。接下来发生的事情尚不清楚——他们的孩子一直在向当局寻求帮助</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 20:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</guid></item></channel></rss>